OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FBright
OL,6,For sunny spells and a chance of
OL,7,Fshowers each day, these more likely on
OL,8,FFriday. Cooler into midweek, with
OL,9,Fpatchy overnight rural frost possible,
OL,10,Fmilder later. Winds generally light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
